          <div class="member-header">
            <h3>Dr. Asher Holzer PhD</h3>
            <p>Chairman</p>
          </div>
          <div class="member-image" style="background-image:url(images/5af47f7993e1c.png)">
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/asher-holzer-15188436/" target="_blank" class="fa fa-linkedin"></a>
          </div>
          <div class="member-desc">
            <p>Asher is a physicist turned serial medical devices entrepreneur with extensive experience in the business of both private and public corporations in the medical device and biotech industry. Asher has a proven track record of taking his innovations public.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    
